milestones.description: Shaun Marsh and Aaron Finch's 245-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 212 between David Boon and Geoff Marsh
This is the highest match aggregate (524) involving teams Australia & Scotland in ODIs

stories.title: Finch, Marsh set up thumping Australia victory
stories.subTitle: Scotland v Australia, Only ODI, Edinburgh
stories.seoTitle: Aaron Finch, Shaun Marsh set up thumping Australia victory
stories.summary: Aaron Finch and Shaun Marsh shared an opening stand of 246 - the second-highest Australian partnership for any wicket in ODIs - in a clinical dissection of Scotland, who were beaten by 200 runs.

stories.title: Scotland's prolonged reality check
stories.subTitle: Scotland v Australia, Only ODI, Edinburgh
stories.summary: Beneath the surface, Scottish cricket is in reasonable health and the signs from the age group teams are promising, but the conversion process is a tough one and years keep passing without any natives making an impact in professional circles
